      <title>特朗普的乐观情绪被对美联储的警惕所取代，比特币暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/bitcoin-slumps-as-trump-euphoria-gives-way-to-wariness-on-fed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美联储的强硬信号促使交易员抛售今年已上涨一倍以上的资产，比特币有望在八周内首次出现七天下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/bitcoin-slumps-as-trump-euphoria-gives-way-to-wariness-on-fed</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 11:44:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普威胁对欧盟征收关税，美联储放缓宽松政策步伐，油价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-december-20</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者权衡美联储降息步伐放缓以及当选总统唐纳德·特朗普威胁对欧盟国家征收关税（除非它们购买更多美国石油和天然气），原油价格下跌，有望连续第周下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-december-20</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 23:31:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：对美联储“严重反应过度”后美国股市上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周最后一个交易日开始一小时后，美国股市走高，表明美联储鹰派立场引发的抛售已经过度。美国国债缩减涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 22:27:05 GMT</pubDate>
